    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<meta name="referrer" content="no-referrer" /><a name="rRVYX"></a># 本地运行JS  得到和浏览器一样的加密数据网站的代码运行的时间轴<br />加载html   加载js  - 运行js初始化 - 用户触发某个事件  - 调用了某段js  - 加密函数 - send（发送，给服务器发送信息） - 接收到服务器数据 - 执行js 解密函数 - 刷新网页渲染  <p>1： 能对网站的js 进行一些调试 <br />能修改js运行当中的一些变量的值  能输出<br />能下断 <br />更智能的监听一些值<br><a name="xA7v8"></a></p><h1 id="Network-区-搜索"><a href="#Network-区-搜索" class="headerlink" title="Network 区 搜索"></a>Network 区 搜索</h1><p>第一个搜索 只能搜索 下面的url<br />第二个搜索和最下的搜索 是搜索全部 区域<br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663053843102-8fc25c17-60d0-4e5f-a609-c1e61e419364.png#clientId=u5668053c-cc6b-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=758&id=u9f86b5a3&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=948&originWidth=1258&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=125781&status=done&style=none&taskId=u49cff5b5-d9ab-4bad-9a06-14de5d89266&title=&width=1006.4" alt="image.png"></p><p>拦截数据包<br />可以查看数据包的内容<br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663140088249-b42b0bf9-a0a2-4122-bdf6-607eca1c1323.png#clientId=u5668053c-cc6b-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=735&id=uc98882a2&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=919&originWidth=1753&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=106820&status=done&style=none&taskId=uc645d08e-2595-43c0-a3b5-2af696d6af6&title=&width=1402.4" alt="image.png"></p><p><a name="mAFBH"></a></p><h1 id="DOM事件和断点"><a href="#DOM事件和断点" class="headerlink" title="DOM事件和断点"></a>DOM事件和断点</h1><p><a name="ySivT"></a></p><h2 id="什么是断点"><a href="#什么是断点" class="headerlink" title="什么是断点"></a>什么是断点</h2><p> 2.1   DOM断点<br />定位的比较准<br />执行的比较靠前  距离加密函数比较远  我们无法根据栈 去快速定位<br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663052866935-5b9937d1-bd6e-4a83-b95f-e179db9c73cc.png#clientId=u148dcfc8-a7f6-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=265&id=uaecbfc55&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=331&originWidth=709&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=76833&status=done&style=none&taskId=u7ecd7024-89ae-4a3a-86a8-ee89ee1c8d3&title=&width=567.2" alt="image.png"><br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663052619213-48e60c36-0f00-4476-a338-16ba3320585d.png#clientId=u148dcfc8-a7f6-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=810&id=u0272f147&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=1012&originWidth=1781&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=303990&status=done&style=none&taskId=u01f9c827-1263-4e14-b7e9-d3fc62c3fc6&title=&width=1424.8" alt="image.png"><br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663053021425-ab1eb727-4736-43be-8172-7997d73e44ed.png#clientId=u148dcfc8-a7f6-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=387&id=u3b9cfdc3&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=484&originWidth=1474&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=58644&status=done&style=none&taskId=u20c3c0bc-0ad7-40b7-81e5-403ac369c38&title=&width=1179.2" alt="image.png"><br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663141553478-0006f1cb-19c8-4ef3-bdca-34d8e85d751b.png#clientId=u0994b74a-3618-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=672&id=u057c6b3d&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=840&originWidth=1519&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=114236&status=done&style=none&taskId=u83a4ae65-f55c-4372-bede-714673bf6a7&title=&width=1215.2" alt="image.png"></p><p>格式化代码格式<br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663141492518-b6c64828-87e9-4c6d-b9c2-bfc6a0fb827c.png#clientId=u0994b74a-3618-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=982&id=u457e28c8&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=1228&originWidth=1874&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=121375&status=done&style=none&taskId=ud1afb32a-edf9-4ec5-8a4b-2c2717f2d22&title=&width=1499.2" alt="image.png"></p><p><a name="nju8E"></a></p><h2 id="DOM事件断点"><a href="#DOM事件断点" class="headerlink" title="DOM事件断点"></a>DOM事件断点</h2><p>xhr 断点<br />代码行断点<br />代码的断点  （debugger）<br />全局事件断点  （浏览器事件断点）<br />异常捕获断点</p><p>断点尝试 <br />断点前先搜索 比较准确<br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663142486966-d845f2c8-f7e2-4817-bacb-4bacbcbaa24d.png#clientId=u0994b74a-3618-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=854&id=u121d3d6c&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=1068&originWidth=2099&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=412931&status=done&style=none&taskId=u18d72654-728f-40d4-a720-c63e8d84606&title=&width=1679.2" alt="image.png"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663142396380-87c0afd1-105f-4ce7-ab9d-d0e2144f5e64.png#clientId=u0994b74a-3618-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=759&id=ue2dca011&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=949&originWidth=1999&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=314148&status=done&style=none&taskId=u3fc79808-ab3f-41fd-97af-e7bd82db319&title=&width=1599.2" alt="image.png"></p><p>简单跟值<br />运行到下一个断点<br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663143258768-269b686c-ad5a-48cf-9ea5-678b3fb76f6a.png#clientId=u0994b74a-3618-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=494&id=u1b84515f&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=617&originWidth=1192&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=106798&status=done&style=none&taskId=u1ee563fa-bef6-435e-8fff-4db4d4fd47f&title=&width=953.6" alt="image.png"></p><p>慢慢跟值<br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663144239586-e63944d9-22bd-42f9-9499-2c274d4ff67d.png#clientId=u0994b74a-3618-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=587&id=ufe81fb3e&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=734&originWidth=466&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=68961&status=done&style=none&taskId=u4a9abf31-3a0c-42e5-9f7f-2c2cdcaabc9&title=&width=372.8" alt="image.png"></p><p><a name="MjuVC"></a></p><h3 id="js的运行顺序"><a href="#js的运行顺序" class="headerlink" title="js的运行顺序"></a>js的运行顺序</h3><p>js 的 运行数据不一定是js文件的编写顺序<br />开始的位置  解析 <br />自执行 方法   ！function() {} ()<br />变量的定义  var xx;<br />赋值语句   a  &#x3D;1 ;<br />方法的调用   xxx()</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs javascript"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">x</span> ()<br>  &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">var</span> a = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-variable language_">console</span>.<span class="hljs-title function_">log</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;x&quot;</span>);<br>  &#125;<br><br>!<span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> (<span class="hljs-params"></span>) &#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-variable language_">console</span>.<span class="hljs-title function_">log</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;!&quot;</span>);<br>&#125;()<br><span class="hljs-title function_">x</span>();<br><span class="hljs-variable language_">console</span>.<span class="hljs-title function_">log</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;1&quot;</span>);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><a name="qAooq"></a></p><h2 id="dom事件断点"><a href="#dom事件断点" class="headerlink" title="dom事件断点"></a>dom事件断点</h2><ol><li>搜索</li></ol><p>定位的位置比较准确，搜到的位置比较多  要自己进行筛选  容易搜不到<br />2 . dom 事件<br />定位得到位置比较靠前</p><p>用户输入明文 ——  经过了一些方法  —— 加密函数    —— 拼装封包 —— 发包函数  ——浏览器的发包函数<br />&#x2F;&#x2F;<br />在调试的时候    想看某个值  必须让断点的位置定位在这一行  才能看到真实的数据<br><a name="DBrYr"></a></p><h1 id="F12调试法和搜索定位法"><a href="#F12调试法和搜索定位法" class="headerlink" title="F12调试法和搜索定位法"></a>F12调试法和搜索定位法</h1><p><a name="UQG8T"></a></p><h2 id="Password"><a href="#Password" class="headerlink" title="Password"></a>Password</h2><p>32 位   16 位   MD5值 <br />40位     sha1 </p><p>看 main  uba  的js文件  <br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663145324779-dbee9be7-d0c5-42c1-96d1-7e9423ae4bf2.png#clientId=u0994b74a-3618-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=751&id=u8e7ebbab&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=939&originWidth=1503&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=204352&status=done&style=none&taskId=u88fbf77d-b4dc-4c88-a6b5-1eec22b60d6&title=&width=1202.4" alt="image.png"></p><p>断点只能 打在  方法   var   定义  加减乘除 上   <br />红色 可以 打 蓝色不能打断点<br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663145785594-1718ce58-3cb9-4618-a8b0-29c20e5d7024.png#clientId=u0994b74a-3618-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=350&id=u5e658a69&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=437&originWidth=729&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=41171&status=done&style=none&taskId=ud3904f93-e00d-4afa-8e52-2d795da4857&title=&width=583.2" alt="image.png"></p><p>栈 <br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663147131454-3771e9e6-17c0-4e57-9b43-f5db87a5019e.png#clientId=u0994b74a-3618-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=732&id=u4b056b46&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=915&originWidth=1411&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=209121&status=done&style=none&taskId=ue766e929-b545-43dc-9455-4c10534eb85&title=&width=1128.8" alt="image.png"><br />密码变成明文  后面就会加密<br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663147174238-4b45638b-4315-4f42-aa06-455304c1a3d7.png#clientId=u0994b74a-3618-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=875&id=ucad9da67&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=1094&originWidth=1766&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=802800&status=done&style=none&taskId=u0d2ada39-d9ff-41bf-a32a-6edaafba566&title=&width=1412.8" alt="image.png"></p><p>变成了密文 的 t<br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663147242433-8cc71556-ca11-4906-8ebe-1a6029bd771f.png#clientId=u0994b74a-3618-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=749&id=u91b42b62&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=936&originWidth=1597&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=545803&status=done&style=none&taskId=u820d3e72-14f9-4ed3-9093-763da5a38d6&title=&width=1277.6" alt="image.png">反括号 (  前 一般都是个方法<br />（） 之间的是参数 <br />所以这里不是对象<br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663147662265-70a3e0d6-2618-4149-9971-7c60b4668ef5.png#clientId=u0994b74a-3618-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=278&id=uc8c827c0&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=347&originWidth=1224&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=144039&status=done&style=none&taskId=u75ff3b73-c308-4f79-9799-77e6b237980&title=&width=979.2" alt="image.png"></p><p> 一步步跳<br />第一步的 密文<br />e给了c   发现是MD5 加密的<br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663148053282-d32e2bcc-1110-4859-9507-74903a3ee03e.png#clientId=u0994b74a-3618-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=258&id=u59e03b03&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=322&originWidth=1183&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=222903&status=done&style=none&taskId=uaee38fd2-983e-4b5a-aab3-03eed8c6c80&title=&width=946.4" alt="image.png"></p><p>第二步 把 t 传给了r   加密成 sha1 <br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663148195464-056f3170-dc4b-4913-938d-44939526e401.png#clientId=u0994b74a-3618-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=193&id=uedf63b94&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=241&originWidth=976&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=155376&status=done&style=none&taskId=u0582ffd8-50df-4f78-9178-1cbe7a48094&title=&width=780.8" alt="image.png"></p><p>第三步 也是 sha1 </p><p><a name="wyJEL"></a></p><h1 id="XHR断点"><a href="#XHR断点" class="headerlink" title="XHR断点"></a>XHR断点</h1><p>好处 ： 定位的位置在发包函数  我们可以跟栈<br />缺点 ： 只能用于xhr的数据包<br />   <br />发包方式 <br />js发包     html 表单发包</p><p>断点方式 ：<br />xhr  breakpoints  进行过滤  支持正则<br />network   面板进行发包函数</p><p>第一种断点方式 <br />根据特征 <br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663160199790-2bd917b4-8896-47d1-8c3a-2d24a46dc94e.png#clientId=u0994b74a-3618-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=626&id=u6826e718&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=783&originWidth=1882&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=493738&status=done&style=none&taskId=u07a79114-02e0-444f-b495-e86aa3374ed&title=&width=1505.6" alt="image.png"><br />然后把   <a href="https://passport.gm99.com/login/login3?callback=jQuery171047872116524409103_1663160058077&encrypt=1&uname=111&password=0ChdIVFzwP8c+Ize9Q2pXE9Qh1x2iqw1lpggSooBifpfWlbhQjkcamWmOfPamyJUDeE52WOcAQhYu8gGRdQ+ebrVcu07ZA45WWoT/lNRr9kcgJ/q45j1TxQcahW3Gd6pSF4Xm0NXB/HCwp74TuAZS7VCu4pT+N8N+IYeGh/tFhk=&remember=checked&ckcode=wr34&_=1663160119409">&#x2F;login&#x2F;login3</a> 复制到XHR 断点哪里<br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663160314904-2ad42b30-1073-406f-a844-38eb1f0ec70b.png#clientId=u0994b74a-3618-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=327&id=u0d897262&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=409&originWidth=707&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=17734&status=done&style=none&taskId=ud608ad05-13dd-43e6-91f7-567e9e4ccf9&title=&width=565.6" alt="image.png"></p><p>第二种<br />和那个栈是一样的<br />jquery  js库 发包<br />点击send  那 <br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663160689100-85f69f38-bf8b-4c28-ac3e-d228612d75d2.png#clientId=u0994b74a-3618-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=777&id=udc1e791f&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=971&originWidth=1919&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=657594&status=done&style=none&taskId=u61b1305b-faec-4206-b816-7d463c1e0d9&title=&width=1535.2" alt="image.png"><br />在这里下断点<br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663160841695-3169dbce-64ec-400f-8787-cf21b859daf3.png#clientId=u0994b74a-3618-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=767&id=uc8315bf3&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=959&originWidth=1794&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=447655&status=done&style=none&taskId=uddf4fd7b-b268-4e03-86d6-97358af49c1&title=&width=1435.2" alt="image.png"></p><p>jquery 都可以过滤掉 <br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663160942871-222b3d33-340d-4f8d-9a34-0d69ad3b5170.png#clientId=u0994b74a-3618-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=263&id=uc5200cc3&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=329&originWidth=557&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=23135&status=done&style=none&taskId=u4b8831af-25bd-49ea-a8de-ed03f360f12&title=&width=445.6" alt="image.png"><br />刚才忘取消刚设置的 断点了<br />点击 login<br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663161861294-8c5fa067-d59e-483f-80e1-90cb7dd7dca4.png#clientId=u0994b74a-3618-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=567&id=u40a8c12f&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=709&originWidth=1393&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=146455&status=done&style=none&taskId=uea6c5e7d-0acb-4e02-8c87-5a72c56e553&title=&width=1114.4" alt="image.png"></p><p>加密内容 下面就是明文<br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663161998554-7d882adc-4fb5-4172-a149-7064b4368e25.png#clientId=u0994b74a-3618-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=531&id=u3c73c2df&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=664&originWidth=1319&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=140197&status=done&style=none&taskId=u72d9d4ed-256d-43e2-a85e-bc5aee62325&title=&width=1055.2" alt="image.png"></p><p><a name="b9V5Y"></a></p><h1 id="hook-定位参数"><a href="#hook-定位参数" class="headerlink" title="hook 定位参数"></a>hook 定位参数</h1><p>1.替换原方法</p><p>覆盖原函数</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs javascript"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">xxx</span>(<span class="hljs-params"></span>)&#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-variable language_">console</span>.<span class="hljs-title function_">log</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;1111&quot;</span>);<br>&#125;<br>xxx = <span class="hljs-keyword">function</span>(<span class="hljs-params"></span>)&#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-variable language_">console</span>.<span class="hljs-title function_">log</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;2222&quot;</span>);<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 覆盖浏览器环境方法<br />改变了系统环境的方法<br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663227809197-ce6c8a6b-c3b9-46ba-9b09-6cca7edf642c.png#clientId=u0994b74a-3618-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=255&id=ufb2457c2&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=319&originWidth=826&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=18235&status=done&style=none&taskId=ua1695278-981c-469b-9dea-a79ab20f2a3&title=&width=660.8" alt="image.png"></p><p><a name="hcmeV"></a></p><h2 id="object-defineProperty-方法"><a href="#object-defineProperty-方法" class="headerlink" title="object.defineProperty() 方法"></a>object.defineProperty() 方法</h2><p>可以通过object.defineProperty() 方法  替换一个对象的属性 <br />属性可能存在的是方法  也有可能存在的是一个值  （getter  ,setter ）</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs javascript">(<span class="hljs-keyword">function</span>(<span class="hljs-params"></span>) &#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">var</span> aaa = <span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span>;<br>  object.<span class="hljs-title function_">defineProperty</span>(<span class="hljs-variable language_">document</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;cookie&#x27;</span>,&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-attr">set</span>:<span class="hljs-keyword">function</span>(<span class="hljs-params">val</span>)&#123;<br>      <span class="hljs-variable language_">console</span>.<span class="hljs-title function_">log</span>(val)<br>      aaa = val;<br>     <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> val;<br>      &#125;,<br>    <span class="hljs-attr">get</span>:<span class="hljs-keyword">function</span>(<span class="hljs-params"></span>)&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> aaa;<br>    &#125;<br>  &#125;);<br>&#125;)();<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><a name="byYss"></a></p><h2 id="hook时机"><a href="#hook时机" class="headerlink" title="hook时机"></a>hook时机</h2><p>在控制台注入的hook 刷新网页就失效了<br />在网页加载第一个js 的位置  第一行下了断点 然后再控制台手动注入hook<br />{有可能注入hook得到时机还是会晚一点}</p><p>2.利用FD的替换响应 ，注入hook<br />这种的时机比较靠前</p><p>爱奇艺   利用 Fiddler  注入hook<br /><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2022/png/22356351/1663232675794-a90ef814-9343-4a1f-adef-ad8de8472307.png#clientId=u0994b74a-3618-4&crop=0&crop=0&crop=1&crop=1&from=paste&height=558&id=u7211afca&margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&name=image.png&originHeight=698&originWidth=1095&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=207714&status=done&style=none&taskId=u1e71a5eb-e934-4138-a6dc-117b3a84de9&title=&width=876" alt="image.png"></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
